import {
  Grid,
  Button,
  Container,
  Stack,
  Typography,
  TextField,
  Divider,
  Card
} from '@mui/material';
// components

import { alpha, styled } from '@mui/material/styles';
import Page from '../../components/Page';

const RootStyle = styled(Card)(({ theme }) => ({
  boxShadow: 'none',
  color: '#000000',
  width: '25%',
  height: '170px'
}));
export default function AppTemperatureGrids() {
  return (
    <Page>
      <Container maxWidth="xl">
        <Grid container spacing={{ xs: 0 }} columns={{ xs: 8, sm: 8, md: 8, lg: 8 }}>
          <RootStyle item xs={2} align="center" style={{ backgroundColor: 'red' }}>
            <Grid
              style={{
                color: '#45a29e',
                borderRadius: '20px',
                top: '10px',
                backgroundColor: 'green',
                width: '90%',
                height: '80%'
              }}
            >
              <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#45a29e' }}>
                Current Temperature:
              </Typography>
            </Grid>
          </RootStyle>
          <RootStyle item xs={2} align="center" style={{ backgroundColor: 'red' }}>
            <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#45a29e' }}>
              minimum Temperature:
            </Typography>
          </RootStyle>
          <RootStyle item xs={2} align="center" style={{ backgroundColor: 'red' }}>
            <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#45a29e' }}>
              Average Temperature:
            </Typography>
          </RootStyle>
          <RootStyle item xs={2} align="center" style={{ backgroundColor: 'red' }}>
            <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#45a29e' }}>
              Maximum Temperature:
            </Typography>
          </RootStyle>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Page>
  );
}
